<subSubSection id="C313657D0E4EFFB5FF7FFBB2FAD7FBDE" box="[151,1293,1116,1141]" pageId="7" pageNumber="108" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="8BB636F60E4EFFB5FF7FFBB2FAD7FBDE" blockId="7.[151,1437,1116,1861]" box="[151,1293,1116,1141]" pageId="7" pageNumber="108">
<emphasis id="B97DEAE40E4EFFB5FF7FFBB2FEC4FBDE" bold="true" box="[151,286,1116,1141]" pageId="7" pageNumber="108">Etymology.</emphasis>
Combination of 
<taxonomicName id="4C094D750E4EFFB5FE34FBB3FDCDFBDF" box="[476,535,1117,1140]" class="Gastropoda" family="Volutidae" genus="Lyria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="7" pageNumber="108" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97DEAE40E4EFFB5FE34FBB3FDCDFBDF" box="[476,535,1117,1140]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="108">Lyria</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with the suffix 
<emphasis id="B97DEAE40E4EFFB5FD20FBB3FCDBFBDF" box="[712,769,1117,1140]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="108">opsis</emphasis>
(resembling in appearance). Gender feminine.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C313657D0E4EFFB5FF2FFB91FBADFA83" pageId="7" pageNumber="108" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8BB636F60E4EFFB5FF2FFB91FD98FB4B" blockId="7.[151,1437,1116,1861]" pageId="7" pageNumber="108">
<emphasis id="B97DEAE40E4EFFB5FF2FFB91FE9BFB33" bold="true" box="[199,321,1151,1176]" pageId="7" pageNumber="108">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
A ventricose 
<emphasis id="B97DEAE40E4EFFB5FE34FB6EFDECFB3C" box="[476,566,1152,1175]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="108">
“ 
<taxonomicName id="4C094D750E4EFFB5FE0CFB6EFDF4FB3C" box="[484,558,1152,1175]" class="Gastropoda" family="Volutidae" genus="Lyria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="7" pageNumber="108" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">Lyria</taxonomicName>
”
</emphasis>
shape with costae slightly opisthocline, rather flexuous in their posterior part, not corresponding from whorl to whorl. Whorls rather depressed, slightly convex, terraced. Four oblique, strong columellar folds. Protoconch bulbous.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB636F60E4EFFB5FF2FFB02FBADFA83" blockId="7.[151,1437,1116,1861]" pageId="7" pageNumber="108">
<emphasis id="B97DEAE40E4EFFB5FF2FFB02FE53FAAE" bold="true" box="[199,393,1260,1285]" pageId="7" pageNumber="108">Included species</emphasis>
. 
<taxonomicName id="4C094D750E4EFFB5FE7FFB03FCFAFAAF" authority="Vredenburg, 1923" authorityName="Vredenburg" authorityYear="1923" box="[407,800,1260,1285]" class="Gastropoda" family="Volutidae" genus="Lyria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="7" pageNumber="108" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="cossmanni">
<emphasis id="B97DEAE40E4EFFB5FE7FFB03FD8AFAAF" box="[407,592,1261,1284]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="108">Lyria cossmanni</emphasis>
