<bibRefCitation id="EF984B070E4EFFB5FC53FADAFBE7FAE7" author="Cox" box="[955,1085,1332,1356]" pageId="7" pageNumber="108" refString="Cox, L. R. (1930) The fossil fauna of the Samana Range and some neighbouring areas. Part 8. The mollusc of the Hangu Shales. Memoirs of the Geological Survey of India, Palaeontologia Indica, New Series, 15, 129 - 222." type="journal article" year="1930">
